x; height:120px; object-fit:cover; border-radius:50%;&#34; alt=&#34;Jiawei Liu&#34; /&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;h3 class=&#34;f4 fw6 mt3 mb1&#34;&gt;Jiawei Liu&lt;/h3&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;p class=&#34;f5 mid-gray&#34;&gt;Director, Violin&lt;/p&gt;</description>
