    <item>
      <title>Sponsors</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/sponsors/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/sponsors/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;We invite businesses, families, and community partners to support this youth-led public celebration honoring the people and groups whose everyday contributions strengthen Lexington through art, technology, storytelling, and civic pride.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;br&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;our-sponsors&#34;&gt;Our Sponsors&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;flex flex-wrap justify-center mt3 mb4&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;w-50-l w-100 pa3 tc&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/images/caellia.png&#34; style=&#34;width:160px; height:160px; object-fit:cover; border-radius:50%;&#34; alt=&#34;Caellia Logo&#34; /&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;h3 class=&#34;f4 fw6 mt2 mb1&#34;&gt;Caellia&lt;/h3&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;https://caellia.com/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; class=&#34;f5 link dim dark-gray&#34;&gt;Learn more →&lt;/a&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;!--&#xD;&#xA;### 🏅 Platinum Sponsors&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;*Be the first Platinum Sponsor! [Contact us](mailto:lyst.connect@gmail.com) to learn more.*&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;---&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;### 🥇 Gold Sponsors&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;*Be the first Gold Sponsor! [Contact us](mailto:lyst.connect@gmail.com) to learn more.*&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;---&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;### 🥈 Silver Sponsors&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;*Be the first Silver Sponsor! [Contact us](mailto:lyst.connect@gmail.com) to learn more.*&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;---&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;### 🥉 Community Sponsors&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;*Be the first Community Sponsor! [Contact us](mailto:lyst.connect@gmail.com) to learn more.*&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;---&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;### 💛 Friends of the Event&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;*Be the first Friend of the Event! [Contact us](mailto:lyst.connect@gmail.com) to learn more.*&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;---&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;br&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;## Sponsorship Levels&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;flex flex-wrap justify-center mt3 mb4&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;w-50-l w-100 pa3&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;ba b--light-silver pa3 br2 h-100&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;h3 class=&#34;f3 fw7 mt0&#34; style=&#34;color:#b5a642;&#34;&gt;🏅 Platinum: $2,000+&lt;/h3&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;ul class=&#34;f5 lh-copy&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;li&gt;Highest logo placement on promotional materials&lt;/li&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;li&gt;Exclusive 30-second featured sponsor display during projection mapping show&lt;/li&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;li&gt;Featured website sponsorship placement&lt;/li&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;li&gt;Logo, name, website link, and QR code&lt;/li&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;li&gt;Recognition during opening remarks and event&lt;/li&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;/ul&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;w-50-l w-100 pa3&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;ba b--light-silver pa3 br2 h-100&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;h3 class=&#34;f3 fw7 mt0&#34; style=&#34;color:#CFB53B;&#34;&gt;🥇 Gold: $1,000+&lt;/h3&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;ul class=&#34;f5 lh-copy&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;li&gt;Major logo placement on website and flyer&lt;/li&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;li&gt;Recognition during opening remarks&lt;/li&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;li&gt;Event signage acknowledgment&lt;/li&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;/ul&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;w-50-l w-100 pa3&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;ba b--light-silver pa3 br2 h-100&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;h3 class=&#34;f3 fw7 mt0&#34; style=&#34;color:#A8A9AD;&#34;&gt;🥈 Silver: $500+&lt;/h3&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;ul class=&#34;f5 lh-copy&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;li&gt;Logo on website and signage&lt;/li&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;li&gt;Public thank-you recognition&lt;/li&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;/ul&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;w-50-l w-100 pa3&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;ba b--light-silver pa3 br2 h-100&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;h3 class=&#34;f3 fw7 mt0&#34; style=&#34;color:#cd7f32;&#34;&gt;🥉 Community: $250+&lt;/h3&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;ul class=&#34;f5 lh-copy&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;li&gt;Name listed on sponsor page and acknowledgments&lt;/li&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;/ul&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;w-50-l w-100 pa3&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;ba b--light-silver pa3 br2 h-100&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;h3 class=&#34;f3 fw7 mt0&#34;&gt;💛 Friend of the Event: $100+&lt;/h3&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;ul class=&#34;f5 lh-copy&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;li&gt;Name listed in supporter appreciation section&lt;/li&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;/ul&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;--&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;br&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;why-sponsor&#34;&gt;Why Sponsor?&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Support youth education and innovation in STEAM&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Increase visibility within the Lexington community&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Align your brand with creativity, leadership, and service&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Celebrate the citizens who make Lexington strong&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;br&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;grants--funding&#34;&gt;Grants &amp;amp; Funding&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;tc mt4 mb4&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/images/CEL_10Years_Final.png&#34; style=&#34;max-width:200px;&#34; alt=&#34;Community Endowment of Lexington&#34; /&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;h3 class=&#34;f4 fw6 mt3&#34;&gt;Community Endowment of Lexington&lt;/h3&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;p class=&#34;f5 lh-copy measure center mid-gray&#34;&gt;&#34;The Community Endowment of Lexington enhances the quality of life for Lexington citizens. CEL awards grants to nonprofits and town agencies working in the areas of health and human services, arts and culture, the environment, and community building.&#34;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
